# Module Purpose

Responsibilities:

- Async Processing
- Scheduled Jobs
- Retry Mechanisms
- Data Synchronization
- Maintenance Tasks

Background Jobs improve reliability and scalability.

---

# Core Principle

Long-running tasks must not execute inside HTTP requests.

---

Bad

Request

↓

Webhook

↓

Sync Orders

↓

Recalculate Dashboard

↓

Send Notifications

↓

Return Response

---

Good

Request

↓

Queue Job

↓

Return Response

↓

Background Worker

↓

Process Task

---

